# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PROFILE - PROFILE PICTURE
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

@AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress = {{$processEnv AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}
@MechanicPersonIdForPicture = 7


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### [Positive][Profile] Get profile picture (200 or 404 if none)
GET {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/profile/picture

###

### [Positive][Profile] Get mechanic profile picture by person id (200 or 404 if none)
GET {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/profile/picture/{{MechanicPersonIdForPicture}}

###

### [Manual][Profile] Open realtime profile picture updates stream (authorized SSE)
GET {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/profile/picture/updates

###

### [Note][Profile] Multipart upload is not supported in .http reliably; use curl for PUT /api/profile/picture
# curl example:
# curl -k -X PUT "{{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/profile/picture" \
#   -H "Cookie: autoservice_at=<ACCESS_COOKIE>; autoservice_rt=<REFRESH_COOKIE>" \
#   -F "file=@C:/path/to/profile-picture.png"
#
# Negative magic-byte checks:
# 1) MIME/content mismatch should return 422.
#    curl -k -X PUT "{{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/profile/picture" \
#      -H "Cookie: autoservice_at=<ACCESS_COOKIE>; autoservice_rt=<REFRESH_COOKIE>" \
#      -F "file=@C:/path/to/image.png;type=image/jpeg"
# 2) Non-image payload with image MIME should return 422.
#    curl -k -X PUT "{{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/profile/picture" \
#      -H "Cookie: autoservice_at=<ACCESS_COOKIE>; autoservice_rt=<REFRESH_COOKIE>" \
#      -F "file=@C:/path/to/not-an-image.txt;type=image/png"

###

### [Positive][Profile] Remove profile picture
DELETE {{AutoService_ApiService_HostAddress}}/api/profile/picture
